{"tid":2371267,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做多一步就可以提升Signal嘅安全性","createTime":"2021-01-18T16:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T06:08:52.000Z","uid":152284,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e968d1065d4d7b879a8b817313f0db5485023fbf","tid":2371267,"uid":152284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:35:02.000Z","msg":"近排見到好多人轉會用Signal。雖然Signal私隱保密程度較高，但係我哋可以透過App內置嘅一啲設定而更進一步提升安全性。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1）撳左上角icon 打開「設定」，<br />\n然後揀選「隱私權」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BeiVnMW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBeiVnMW.png&h=01c88d65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2）開啟「註冊鎖」、「螢幕鎖定」同「開啟程式轉換時隱藏畫面功能」，並且將「螢幕鎖定逾時」較「即時」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zttBRLi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzttBRLi.png&h=89bdc459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣就算行行下街俾癲狗咬走咗部手機，你同你朋友寶貴嘅對話都唔會咁容易比人破解。<br />\n<br />\n祝香港人平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d7bcf5389bdff1d2a51bbfb83b7837f942e648","tid":2371267,"uid":152284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:35:36.000Z","msg":"自推十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374a35ad32b4cd2c4ccfb8f0c6d2617d7e85f32a","tid":2371267,"uid":152284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:35:47.000Z","msg":"自推十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948f57ea3e9423dc35f8ddcb640db55b33f4a9f4","tid":2371267,"uid":152284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:35:59.000Z","msg":"自推十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0f3d924250bdf24d04c0e8aff1a6b0747dbb77","tid":2371267,"uid":152284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:36:09.000Z","msg":"自推十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.g